@startuml
title Context Diagram: AI Edge-to-Cloud System (with Monitoring)

actor "System Operator" as User
actor "Edge Device" as Edge

rectangle "AI Edge-to-Cloud System" as System {

    note top
    Core system functions:
    - Edge Devices capture frames & perform inference
    - Kafka messaging layer transports events
    - Server aggregates data
    - Monitoring / Data Access included: view aggregated data locally or via cloud
    end note
}

' --------------------
' Interactions
' --------------------
Edge --> System : sends detection events
User --> System : monitors and views aggregated data

' --------------------
' Notes
' --------------------
note right of Edge
Edge device can be a laptop, Raspberry Pi, or similar
Handles hardware-specific processing (e.g., camera)
Data is sent via standardized Docker / Kafka pipeline
end note

note left of User
System operator views aggregated data
via web interface (local or cloud)
end note

@enduml






